{"tid":1449390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:46.000Z","uid":3357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6c538ab3144ae282b7ee364dee7890b442489543","tid":1449390,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=92da788d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=49e195c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}